title: Emily Davison with Kate Willoughby
itunes:title: Emily Davison with Kate Willoughby
itunes:subtitle: In this episode, originally released in 2018, Dan talks to actor, activist, and "part-time suffragette" Kate Willoughby about Emily Davison, the centenary of the Representation of the People Act, and what still needs to be done.
